         python3-audioop-lts
Recommends: ffmpeg
Description: high-level audio manipulation library for Python
 Pydub provides a simple, high-level interface for working with audio
 files: slicing, concatenating, mixing, fading, and exporting. Format
 conversion (MP3, OGG, WAV, FLAC, AAC, etc.) is handled by ffmpeg.
 .
 Pure Python with no mandatory dependencies. Useful in game development
 for procedural audio assembly, automated sound effect processing,
 batch format conversion, and audio pipeline tooling.
